What you need to know:

I know Kenyans have a pitiable reading culture. In fact, a very tiny section of the population buys books for personal consumption. Still, I would encourage Oliech to write a book, or at least tell his story, his side of the story in a comprehensive TV interview. The tell it all with Oprah Winfrey, or in our case, Grace Msalame.I can tell you Dennis the Menace, you will be a hit, just like you were in your marauding days as a football striker.